  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\nApply the intended design to name+image editing under \"Profile\" on Status Desktop.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n<img width=\"244\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-21 a la s 9 48 13 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45867326-7ec4eb00-bd83-11e8-91ad-72dc96ad0090.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n<img width=\"327\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-21 a la s 9 47 05 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45867263-56d58780-bd83-11e8-928f-6d5a6d109452.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Solution\r\n- [ ] Apply blinking cursor \r\n- [ ] Apply italic style to font\r\n- [ ] Make image editable\r\n- [ ] Apply overlay and icon on image\r\n- [ ] Remove the name's grey background when on edit mode (temp workaround before https://github.com/status-im/react-native-desktop/issues/338 will be fixed):\r\n<img width=\"104\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-21 a la s 9 54 54 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45867736-6a352280-bd84-11e8-898d-7287e04eb424.png\">\r\n\r\n- [ ] Apply bigger target area to \"Edit/Done\" action. Right now is hard to click:\r\n<img width=\"649\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-09-21 a la s 9 51 59 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/45867598-162a3e00-bd84-11e8-85c4-8ed8ca76c177.png\">\r\n\r\n- [ ] Put focus to the editable area when the user is in editable mode\r\n\r\nWhen you open Profile -> Edit you should manually set focus to username field. Now it is looking a bit confusing, especially when area is not distinguished from background.\r\nI'm suggesting to set focus automatically to username area when you click on \"Edit\" (like it is made for mobile)\r\nVideo: http://take.ms/8A5ok\r\n\r\n*State:* \r\nblocked by RN issue: https://github.com/status-im/react-native-desktop/issues/338\r\n\r\n- [ ]  Input area is not aligned according to design.\r\n\r\n![px](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/45752722-1e1c9d80-bc1f-11e8-8c8a-59a098b950e1.png)\r\n\r\n- [ ] Username is cut in editable mode when it contains emoji\r\n![emoji](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/45753475-b287ff80-bc21-11e8-9947-a675b569306a.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Designs in Zeplin** >> zpl.io/brE1NdX\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Profile\r\n- Click on \"Edit\" (top right corner)",
